properties.Name: EquipmentType
properties.Description:
A categorization of assets that are defined as 'equipment' for use in a variety of activities including manufacturing, transportation, shipping and storage.

Ex:
- Belt loader
- Bulk cargo cart
- Cargo loader
- Dolly
- Tank
- Trailer
- Vat
- Fire protection equipment
- Pumps
- Compensators
- Compressors
- Boiler equipment
- Heat exchangers
- Filter systems for liquids and gases
- Water treatment and cleaning systems
- Energy equipment
- Mixers

Columns.Name: EquipmentTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an equipment type.

Columns.Name: EquipmentTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of an equipment type.

Columns.Name: EquipmentTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an equipment type.
